, and 
\begin_inset Formula $\v b$
\end_inset

 for the corresponding normal equation in terms of the data 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{i}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $y_{i}$
\end_inset

 and the unknowns 
\begin_inset Formula $r$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $s$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

